Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for cases ending with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in cases of re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time to reach Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR from the start of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time between Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR in comparison to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total time for Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR grouped by org:resource
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource
